name: 21OZ Natural Canned Pumpkin Powder - 100% Pure Vegetable Powder, No Added Sugar & High in Fibre, Pumpkin for Juice, Smoothie, Baking, Pie, Soup
short_description: 100% Pure Vegetable Powder: Our 100% natural pumpkin powder is made from fresh pumpkins, carefully dehydrated at low temperatures and ground into a fine powder, preserving its rich nutrients and natural sweetness. With no additives or no added sugars, it's an easy way to enhance your recipes, bringing deliciousness and health to your family and friends!

21OZ Pumpkin Powder: Our pumpkin powder comes in a generous 600g package, providing ample quantity for all your cooking and baking needs. Perfect for creating a variety of delicious recipes, this substantial size ensures you'll always have enough on hand to add that delightful pumpkin flavor to your favorite dishes!

Versatile Seasoning: The versatile uses of pumpkin powder make it an essential ingredient in any kitchen. You can add it to your baking recipes to create delicious pumpkin pies, muffins, and breads. It's also perfect for making drinks like pumpkin smoothies and oatmeal. Additionally, pumpkin powder can serve as a flavor enhancer for soups and stews, giving your dishes a rich, autumnal taste.

Natural Coloring Agent: Pumpkin powder is not only a delicious ingredient but also a natural coloring agent that can add a charming golden hue to your foods and beverages. Its vibrant color makes it an ideal choice for healthy eating. Using pumpkin powder as a coloring agent not only enhances the visual appeal but also boosts nutritional value, ensuring that every bite is filled with natural flavor and color!

Storage Suggestions: To maintain the freshness and flavor of the pumpkin powder, please store the canned pumpkin powder in a cool, dry place, away from direct sunlight. It is recommended to tightly close the lid after opening to prevent moisture and air from entering, ensuring the best quality and taste.
